talent level 20 upgrade Iron Charge
increase the damage when stun by 25
increase the scaling strenght when stun by 15%
increase armor gain while in charge by 10
increase health regeneration gain per hit 0.8
reduce coldown by 5
reduce mana cost by 25

add a new modifier Holy Charge
While he is Charging, he will Ignore all form of range attacks and reflect them back at them, those range attack reflect will only
deal 40% of its damage and effect, if Xarofos pass on any allys when Charging, he will heal them by 10% of their max health and give
them 35% of the armor he gain when he is charging for 10 seconds, Upon finishing the charge at the target location, he will cast Iron
Blast with all of its effect and dealing 50% increase damage as well, enemys will also be force to attack him for 2.5 seconds and for
the duration they attack him, they will do 40% less damage to him, Each enemys hit with Iron Charge will increase its base damage by 1
up to 25 bonus damage, at 20 bonus damage Xarofos will gain 10% damage reduction and 100 movespeed also gaining Phase, With the Phase
bonus he will deal 15% of his strenght into damage when he pass inside of enemys, can only happen every 10 seconds, work with the charge
as well.


